{"word":"ἐνδύω","slug":"ἐνδύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνδύω</b></el> <el>(and <el>-δύνω</el>) (with <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <el>ἐνδύομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-δύσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>-εδυσάμην</el>) (and aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>-έδυν</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <i>to go into</i>, <p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>of clothes, <i>to put on</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>induere sibi</el>, <el>ἔνδυνε χιτῶνα</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>πέπλον</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ἐνδέδυκα</el>, <i>to wear</i> <el>κιθῶνας</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to put on, assume</i> the person of . . , <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to enter, to press into</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—also, <el>ἐνδ. εἰς . .</el> , <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to enter</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>Causal in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> <el>ἐνδύω</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-δύσω</el>, aor1 <el>-έδυσα</el><a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>induere alicui, to put on</el> another, <i>to clothe in</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to clothe</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}